snippet.title: Family Stadium 2003 (GameCube) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of Family Stadium 2003, a baseball video game by Namco for the Nintendo GameCube. Yomiuri Giants at Namco All-Stars, at the Klonoa Stadium. 

A lot of baseball games are hard when you're first starting out on them, but man, I got my butt kicked by the CPU about four times before this recording, where I moved down to the easiest difficulty and still got mostly outplayed. For a friendly-looking arcade-style baseball game, they make you work for this one.
